lead_paragraph: Barcelona's Circuit de Catalunya will host a round of the MotoGP world championship until at least 2021 after agreeing a five-year contract extension, promoters Dorna said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Barcelona Circuit to Host MotoGP to 2021
